       23
************************ Turbine characteristics *********************
Turbine
A = N/sqrt(T03)
B = m*sqrt(T03)/P03
C = P03/P04
E = Fraction
N = Rotational speed [rev/min]
P03 = Total pressure at Turbine inlet  [Bar]
P04 = Total pressure at Turbine outlet  [Bar]
T03 = Total temperature at Turbine inlet  [K]
m   = mass flow [kg/s]
************************* Conversion factors *************************
       1       (A_fact) To convert to  [rev/s]/sqrt[K]
       1     (B_fact) To convert to  [kg/s]*sqrt[K]/Bar
       1    (C_fact) To convert to  pressure ratio
       1   (E_fact) To convert to  fraction
           1   Inertia
           0   Option (0 = list eff vs nondim. mass flow, 1= list eff vs. speed)
        2007  (Gas constant)
           0  (Gas Constant scaling)
           0  (total-total/total-static option, 0 = total-total, 1 = total-static)
           0  (exit area)
           0   Shaft Work Calculation Option(0 = Use Efficiency, 1 = Use Corrected work)
           1  (Corrected work scaling factor)
